courses.entryRequirements: A completed undergraduate degree (or equivalent) + meet English language requirements. English (typical course requirement): IELTS 6.5 overall with Writing 6.0 (atau TOEFL iBT ~81 with corresponding sub-scores). Indonesia (SMA): calon Indonesia harus memenuhi persyaratan nilai SMA (rata-rata pada 6 mata pelajaran kelas 12) dan persyaratan bahasa Inggris; jika belum memenuhi syarat akademik, pathway diterima melalui Foundation providers yang diakui (mis. Trinity College Foundation Studies).

Recent secondary education (VCE/IB/A-levels) or recognised equivalent. Entry is selection-rank (ATAR) based for domestic; international applicants (Indonesia – SMA) must meet required Year 12 averages (rata-rata nilai 6 mata pelajaran kelas 12) and English language requirements; prerequisites may apply for some streams. Jika belum memenuhi syarat SMA, pathway yang diterima termasuk program Foundation yang diakui (mis. Trinity College Foundation Studies).
courses.duration: 3–4 years full-time (lihat opsi dan kombinasi program di halaman kursus)

courses.entryRequirements: Applicants must have completed an undergraduate degree or equivalent qualification. Selection is based on prior academic performance and may also consider relevant professional experience and/or admission test results where applicable. English language requirement: IELTS Academic overall score 7.5 with a minimum of 7.0 in each band (Writing, Speaking, Reading, Listening), or TOEFL iBT overall score 100 with minimum sub-scores of Writing 26, Speaking 24, Reading 22, and Listening 22, in accordance with the official University of Melbourne Juris Doctor entry requirements.

Recent secondary education (VCE/IB/A-levels) or equivalent. Entry selection via selection rank (ATAR) for domestic; international applicants must meet the required Year 12 averages and English language requirements. If not meeting direct entry, recognised foundation pathways (eg. Trinity College Foundation Studies) are available.
courses.duration: 3 years full-time (dapat dipadukan menjadi double degree)
courses.fees: AUD 37,884 - 52,032 per EFTSL (2025 indicative international tuition range); typical total course fee estimate: AUD 100,868 - 168,170 (first year / typical load estimates).
